                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Starvation."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " A terrible blight afflicted your rural village, and many of your friends and family members starved to death. You survived, but only barely."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
