                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Disfigurement."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " One of your arcane experiments went wrong and scarred or dismembered you so gravely that others now shun you. Only the Volstrucker showed you kindness after that day."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
